---
import IconFacebook from "@/assets/icons/IconFacebook.astro"
import IconInstagram from "@/assets/icons/IconInstagram.astro"
import IconTikTok from "@/assets/icons/IconTikTok.astro"
---

<div class="brand-story__content">
  <h2 class="brand-story__title">Nuestra Historia</h2>
  <p class="brand-story__description">
    Degoro nació del deseo de conectar a las comunidades artesanales colombianas con personas que valoran la autenticidad y la historia detrás de cada prenda. Cada pieza que creamos es un puente entre la tradición y la moda contemporánea.
  </p>
</div>

<footer>
  <div class="container">
      <div class="contact">
        <h3 class="heading">Contacto</h3>
        <ul class="contact-list">
          <li><a href="mailto:hola@degoro.com">hola@degoro.com</a></li>
          <li><a href="tel:+5712345678">+57 1 234 5678</a></li>
          <li>Bogotá, Colombia</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="social">
        <h3 class="heading">Síguenos</h3>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook" class="social-link">
            <IconFacebook size={100} color="var(--color-secondary-light)" />
          </a>
          <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram" class="social-link">
            <IconInstagram size={100} color="var(--color-secondary-light)" />
          </a>
          <a href="#" aria-label="TikTok" class="social-link">
            <IconTikTok size={100} color="var(--color-secondary-light)" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom">
      <small>&copy; 2026 Degoro. Todos los derechos reservados.</small>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  footer {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-smoke-white);
    padding: var(--space-12) 0 var(--space-6);
  }

  .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-secondary-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-1);
  }

  .contact-list a {
    color: var(--color-smoke-white);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .contact-list a:hover {
    color: var(--color-secondary-light);
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .social-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    aspect-ratio: 1/1;
    transition: background-color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .social-link:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-primary-light);
    border-color: var(--color-smoke-white);
  }

  .bottom {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(245, 243, 239, 0.15);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .bottom small {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-secondary-light);
  }
</style>
